      propertyPath: speakerImage.Array.size
      value: 3
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 320530506433659665, guid: a1c123b23fa093646a93015aa00ecc2d,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: messageText.Array.data[0]
      value: So are what you two doing here anyways? Don't tell me yer here for Bucky's
        hook...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 320530506433659665, guid: a1c123b23fa093646a93015aa00ecc2d,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: messageText.Array.data[1]
      value: Uhh who's Bucky? We're here for The Legendary World-Renowned Gold-Plated
        Ruby Hook!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 320530506433659665, guid: a1c123b23fa093646a93015aa00ecc2d,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: messageText.Array.data[2]
      value: Blast! That's Bucky's hook!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 320530506433659665, guid: a1c123b23fa093646a93015aa00ecc2d,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: messageText.Array.data[3]
      value: ...What does that mean?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 320530506433659665, guid: a1c123b23fa093646a93015aa00ecc2d,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: messageText.Array.data[4]
      value: I'm a cursed object, only a fool would pick me up. Just like your hook
        there, you're stuck with me forever now.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 320530506433659665, guid: a1c123b23fa093646a93015aa00ecc2d,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: messageText.Array.data[5]
      value: Use the LEFT MOUSE BUTTON to throw me, and use LEFT MOUSE BUTTON again
        to call me back. Try throwing me at that landlubber over there.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
